{"tid":1177374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多國出聲!!] 英國,美國,德國,加拿大,馬來西亞,奧地利議員聯署公開信 促林鄭撤回「送中」修訂","createTime":"2019-05-29T18:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T08:39:29.000Z","uid":172274,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d21c04181c0bd5fa2f8ccc8538952ac722cb24f9","tid":1177374,"uid":172274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8QKgSp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8QKgSp.png&h=d72ea457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZudzD5Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZudzD5Q.png&h=2766ee48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i5dLLLS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi5dLLLS.png&h=8071add4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯署比林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯署議員分別是<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英國上議院議員大衛阿爾頓（David Alton）<br />\n英國下議院議員兼自由民主黨黨鞭卡邁克爾（Alistair Carmichael）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />德國議員Katrin G&ouml;ring-Eckardt<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加拿大議員兼副影子外交大臣Garnett Genuis<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬來西亞議員兼「東盟人權議員組織」（ASEAN Parliamentarians for Human Rights）主席查爾斯聖地亞哥（Charles Santiago）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奧地利的歐洲議會議員Josef Weidenholzer<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />7名美國眾議員及1名美國參議員<br />\n<br />\n國際社會持續發聲反對港府修訂《逃犯條例》。「香港監察」昨天發佈一封15名來自多個國家的議員聯署信，要求特首林鄭月娥考慮撤回修訂草案，並探討其他方法解決逃犯問題。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信指，他們認同陳同佳案須尋求公義，但相信可透過法律學者及議員提出的替代方案處理，此舉亦可讓香港有更多時間考慮進一步改革，並最終達致一個符合《中英聯合聲明》所保護的基本人權和法治的一個解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n他們認為，香港的成功建基於健全的法治和自由，現行的引渡法例本身設立了一道中港防火牆，有助捍衞香港法治；英國解密檔案亦顯示，中英雙方當年討論回歸時認同有需要維持這道防火牆。他們續稱，香港是連接中國與世界的重要據點，也是中國最重要的資金提供者和直接投資者；國際社會對香港的法治和自治的信心，屬於所有聯署國家的重要利益，所以希望林鄭可以考慮撤回方案並探討其他選擇。"},{"pid":"c4a110b85a8904e4aff18d088928565522cb3dfb","tid":1177374,"uid":33829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:36:51.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ed5f9475db7b0cc9a838c8859ef6deaf8180743f","tid":1177374,"uid":172274,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:43:37.000Z","msg":"其實5日前美國8個跨黨議員已經發過信比林鄭, 但佢唔聽。<br />\n<br />\n今日全世界更多國家出聲警告。愈黎愈大件事!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190525/s00001/1558743295902/【逃犯條例】美國8名參眾議員聯署信予林鄭月娥-促撤《逃犯條例》修訂\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190525%2Fs00001%2F1558743295902%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B8%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BF%A1%E4%BA%88%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E4%BF%83%E6%92%A4%E3%80%8A%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuichR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=c078ad27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190525%2Fs00001%2F1558743295902%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B8%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BF%A1%E4%BA%88%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E4%BF%83%E6%92%A4%E3%80%8A%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82&h=fd137ac0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190525/s00001/1558743295902/【逃犯條例】美國8名參眾議員聯署信予林鄭月娥-促撤《逃犯條例》修訂</a>"},{"pid":"fcf08098b84bc2d60817784d42c6c2273a7ed21c","tid":1177374,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T18:45:06.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"bb036a6173f0d540e0dc9a893c47d0be2260373